# digest/

<!-- Landing zone for n8n daily digest PRs.
     Files here are created automatically by the n8n daily-digest workflow at 3 AM.
     The PM reviews the PR each morning and merges if content looks correct.
     On merge, digest-router.yml routes each row to docs/ or memory/ automatically.
     This folder is a staging area — it does not accumulate.
     Format: YYYY-MM-DD.csv with header: type;project;title;content -->
